content: Its good but it only caters for guitar and violins natively. To be a truly great tuner it needs to cater for all transposing instruments too like Bb and Eb brass. This is what a previous poster meant by a chromatic tuner. So when a Bb instrument plays a C, it shows a C not Bb. This would allow many more people to be interested in it, not just violin and guitar players.
replyContent: Thank you for the feedback! The other reviewer meant something a bit different (explained the details via mail), but your suggestion about the transposing instruments is great too, definitely will add it in one of the next versions.
